{"word":"ὑπερπερισσεύω","slug":"ὑπερπερισσεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπερπερισσεύω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπέρ\">ὑπέρ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περισσεύω\">περισσεύω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘be in extraordinary amount’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>abound <a href='B:520 5:20'>Ro 5:20</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to abound in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b>bestow without measure,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> be made to abound, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a>, and so in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <el>ὑπερπερισσεύομαι τῇ χαρᾷ</el> I am overflowing with joy <b><a href='B:540 7:4'>2 Cor 7:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπεροχή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπερπερισσῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}